<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="same-adj">same <strong><em>adj</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /seɪm/    美 /seɪm/  </p>
<p>[只用于名词前] [无比较级变化，常与the连用]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>同一的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Don’t forget to return the book to the same place where you found it. 
别忘了把书放回原处。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>the very same + n:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The two teachers have told us the very same joke. 
两位老师给我们讲了个完全一样的笑话。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>the same ... as / wh-从句：</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The teacher gave me the same advice as he did last time. 
老师给了我和上次相同的建议。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It was the same place where I had experienced many things — floods of memories went through my mind. 
正是在此地我经历了许多事情，无数回忆涌上心头。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>同样的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Men and women now get the same pay for doing the same jobs. 
现在男女同工同酬。</p></div></div>